data.description: This sun-filled and immaculate end-unit townhome sits within the gates of Carmel Valley Ranch along the 15th Fairway with sweeping views across to the 18th. Graced with a natural warm palette that flows seamlessly out to the magnificent view-scape, this refreshed and meticulously maintained Carmel retreat is ready to move into and enjoy. The bright open floorplan features large view windows and soaring white-washed vaulted ceilings. There is a large first-floor primary French-inspired suite and two upstairs ensuite bedrooms with mountain views. The kitchen has new stainless-steel appliances, granite counters, and taupe cabinets. A separate den has sand-blasted Mexican tile floors, garden views, and a half-bath. Wood floors are in the LR, DR, and primary suite. The outdoor space offers a private courtyard, a golf course patio, and a large entertainment garden patio. Nearby are golf, tennis, hiking, dining, and the resort's fun-filled amenities. Come and enjoy mid-valley's coveted sunshine!
